{"tid":465938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那STYLE】 天貓店鴨頸店「鮮·嫩·多汁，想要嗎」意淫廣告","createTime":"2017-11-12T05:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T13:02:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f1f0e06ededdd0fd2733f762bdc50b53cefcb1","tid":465938,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.caogenzz.com/Uploads/Images/Contents/2017/11/09/gcHVUaMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caogenzz.com%2FUploads%2FImages%2FContents%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2FgcHVUaMu.jpg&h=e99d09d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商家為了吸睛，可以去得幾盡？內地一家出售鴨脖食品的公司「絕味鴨脖」在本月1日於其天貓旗艦店上，推出了一張「雙11」預熱海報。惟該海報卻被轟低俗及消費女性，最終公司將海報下架兼道歉。豈料，公司未有擺休，繼續在官方微信公眾號上，推出含性暗示的廣告，繼而捱轟。<br />\n<br />\n該則題為《我不搞預售，我就是玉獸》的廣告，用對話形式進行推銷。廣告被網民炮轟，直至昨日，相關網絡新聞報道達497篇，微博1181條，微信文章101篇，論壇文章114篇，APP推送199篇。事後有網民批評「絕味鴨脖」手法低俗，直言要杯葛公司產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171110/3d0b491a9e3e43f8be69ddb7bbc797a2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20171110%2F3d0b491a9e3e43f8be69ddb7bbc797a2.jpeg&h=a78f2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早於本月1日，有網友發現絕味鴨脖天貓店的營銷海報上，有漫畫人物穿著一條紅色內褲躺著，雙腳卻戴著鎖鏈。海報更寫有「鮮&middot;嫩&middot;多汁，想要嗎」「抵不住的誘惑」等意淫字眼，最終海報被撤。"},{"pid":"0793971d6bab514e17a3b300388bcc991fb85ce8","tid":465938,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"用心做鴨呢句都夠用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e05c8443a4412ae5d4fae10ce242c1d407be881","tid":465938,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用心做鴨呢句都夠用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56bfec33cdd7ae75ea23eeeba64e107afe6df3c","tid":465938,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"曲線幫人宣傳"}]}